quote.summary: Zhenro Services Group Ltd is a company primarily engaged in the provision of property management services. The Company mainly operates four businesses. The property management services business is engaged in providing property management services, including cleaning services, security services, landscaping services, repair and maintenance services for both residential and non-residential properties and commercial properties. The value-added services to non-property owners business is engaged in providing sales assistance services, housing repair services and others. The community value-added services business is engaged in providing home-living services, car park management, leasing assistance and other services. The commercial operational management services business is engaged in providing brand and management output services, sublease services and others. The Company mainly conducts its business in the domestic market.
